	<h4 class="text-center">Accidental Causes </h4>
	<p style="font-size: 130%;">As human age they suffer a decline in their <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cognition">cognitive</a> capabilities directly effecting driving abilities. Although by adopting safe driving practices and mitigating risk factors it is very much possible to keep driving deep into our old years. The important thing is to lookout for signs which indicate that age is interfering with ones driving abilities and adjust accordingly. This page will provide a comprehensive coverage on the likely causes of elderly driver accidents and achievable ways of increasing their safety.
	</p>
